Subject: Your FedEx Package is on the Way!

Dear [Recipient],

We are excited to inform you that your package is now in transit and on its way to you! Your FedEx tracking number is: 1234567890.

Estimated delivery date: [Insert estimated delivery date]

Package contents: [Brief description of contents]

Please note that a signature may be required upon delivery. You can track the status of your package in real-time by visiting the FedEx website and entering your tracking number.

If you have any questions or concerns about your shipment, please do not hesitate to contact our customer service team at 1-800-GO-FEDEX.

Thank you for choosing FedEx for your shipping needs. We appreciate your business and look forward to delivering your package to you soon.

Warm regards,
The FedEx Team
